General.Name: Aura FAT Projects Acquisition Corp Class A Ordinary Shares
General.Description: Aura FAT Projects Acquisition Corp does not have significant operations. The company intends to effect a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It focuses on acquiring technology companies with Web 3.0, blockchain, cryptocurrency, digital ledger, e-gaming, and other new financial technology and services application in Southeast Asia, Australia, and New Zealand. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Singapore.
